Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:37.23,Tomohisa,NTP,0,0,0,,早安  小圓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:38.35,Madoka,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.70,0:04:41.34,Tomohisa,NTP,0,0,0,,達也去叫她了  去幫忙吧
