Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:12.67,Homura,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:15.58,Madoka,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？  嗯 是沒錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:21.84,Madoka,NTP,0,0,0,,我是說那個…  難道你知道在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.77,0:12:31.93,Madoka,NTP,0,0,0,,…曉美同學？
